   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Parent Support for Children with Hearing Loss</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In addition to providing clinical services to children with hearing loss, PRC also offers counseling, therapy and training to parents to educate parents on their options, provide emotional support, improve the parent-child relationship and communication, and reinforce interventions in the home all to achieve the best possible outcomes for the child. Our goal is to be able to increase our outreach and provide these support programs free-of-charge to families in the Washington, DC region.</narrative>
  </description>
